    DDRB is 8 bits: [unused:unused:DDB5:DDB4:DDB3:DDB2:DDB1:DDB0]
    1<<DDB4: sets bit DDB4 (data-direction, port B, 4th pin), which puts pin 3 on ATtiny85 in output mode;
